messages.message: I just used adobe print to PDF
A lot of web pages would be stored as PDF this way, no?
Would ‘Force Image OCR’ fix this automatically?
Yes ‘Force Image OCR’ should likely fix this. Doing force image OCR on all machine readable/ partially machine readable documents would be quite costly latency wise though.

In the normal IB is that if a PDF is passed in, and if the OCR cannot find a certain amount of characters it turns on Force OCR automatically - is there an argument to add an additional clause to this if there is additionally no legible words either?
